text: Brune Poirson (born 1 September 1982) is an American-born French politician. She was Secretary of State to the Minister for the Ecological and Inclusive Transition since 2017. On March 14, 2020 Poirson was the second French government official to test positive for COVID-19. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:French politicians Category:Politicians from Washington, D.C.
title: Brune Poirson
